Package: DBpower
Type: Package
Title: Finite sample power calculations for detection boundary tests
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
	person("Ryan", "Sun", email = "ryansun.work@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre”))
Description: Calculates lower bound on power, upper bound on power, and exact power (small sets only) for detection boundary tests (e.g. Berk-Jones, Higher-Criticism, Generalized erk-Jones, Generalized Higher-Criticism) used in set-based inference studies. 
